Babygrande Records is pleased to announce it has signed a deal with Liquid Swords Entertainment for the next release from

Wu-Tang's GZA/Genius.

Tentatively entitled, GZA Presents, this release will be the official GZA/Genius Mixtape and is scheduled for release later this year.

Additional film and music projects are also being discussed.

GZA has been selling out shows up and down the east coast but that didnt stop him from from taking some time to get up with RZA to discuss GZA Presents, which will be in stores later this year on Liquid Swords/Babygrande.

You can also check out GZA on Jus Allah's new album, All Fates Have Changed which will be in stores June 7th.

Stay tuned to www.gza-genius.com (coming soon) for more information.
